About this demo

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]

This demo has been designed to show you how Houzez is flexible and able to accommodate forms to generate leads. All the multistep forms havebeen created using Gravity Formsthat it's required in order to have this demo fully functional.

Gravity Formsis a premium WordPressplugin thatrequires a license key to be activated. The license key won't be included if you buyHouzez, but it requires to be purchased separately.

Please note we used Gravity Form because, in our opinion, is one of the best plugins to create lead capture forms. We don't receive any commission if you choose to buy a Gravity Form license. Our recommendation is based on the quality of the productand is not based on any compensation.
